reviewText: I am a big fan of Nick, especially of Kingdom. But I was deeply disappointed in this dvd, as it was only comprised of interviews at radios stations. There is a brief voice over narration between each interview. The title of this dvd does no come close to the content.
Nick is very good actor looks are hot and just good movie to see recommend recommended for others
Just some videos posted on YouTube.  Zach Sang's radio interview, an interview by HOT 97, etc.  I'll give it two stars, because it's a good selection of interviews.
Absolute waste of money. It's just video shot during a few radio station interviews promoting Nick's CD.
